longInfo:
Passport required.
- Passports and other documents accepted for entry must be
  valid for at a minimum of 3 months beyond the period of
  intended stay. 
Admission and Transit Restrictions:
- Admission and transit refused to holders of passports issued
  by Congo (Dem. Rep.) , other than "B"-series (i.e., "OB",
  "SB", "DB") passports. 

Visa required. 

- Information on Schengen visas 
Minors:
- Infants aged up to 6 months, of a visa required nationality
   
Additional Information:
- Valid visas in full, invalidated travel documents are
  accepted if accompanied by a new travel document. 
- Passengers entering Austria on a one-way ticket
  
Warning:
- Passports and/or passport replacing documents issued more
  than 10 years prior to date of travel are not accepted. 
- Visitors not holding return/onward ticket could be refused
  entry
